getPopularPhotos

public PhotoList getPopularPhotos(Date date,
                                  StatsInterface.SORT sort,
                                  int perPage,
                                  int page)
                           throws IOException,
                                  org.json.JSONException,
                                  FlickrException
getPopularPhotos

Parameters:
date - Stats will be returned for this date. This should be in either be in YYYY-MM-DD or unix timestamp format. A day according to Flickr Stats starts at midnight GMT for all users, and timestamps will automatically be rounded down to the start of the day. If no date is provided, all time view counts will be returned.
sort - The order in which to sort returned photos. Defaults to views. The possible values are views, comments and favorites.
perPage - Number of referrers to return per page. If this argument is omitted, it defaults to 25. The maximum allowed value is 100.
page - The page of results to return. If this argument is omitted, it defaults to 1.
Returns:
Throws:
IOException
org.json.JSONException
FlickrException
